#!/bin/sh
GREPWORD=Treffer
#GREPWORD=contentholder
#GREPWORD=centerColumn
TEMPFILE=$(mktemp "/tmp/leo.XXXXXX") || exit 1
trap "rm -f $TEMPFILE" EXIT
if wget \
        --quiet \
        http://dict.leo.org/?search=$1 \
        --output-document=/dev/stdout | grep -i $GREPWORD > $TEMPFILE
        # --output-document=/dev/stdout > $TEMPFILE
        # | grep -i "Treffer" > $TEMPFILE
then
    w3m -T text/html -dump $TEMPFILE | less
else
    echo "'$1' not found in leo" >&2
fi
